#. module: l10n_be_hr_payroll
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:l10n_be_hr_payroll.field_hr_payslip_employee_depature_holiday_attests__net_n
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Taking into account for remuneration:\n"
"            - Fixed and variable remuneration\n"
"            - Overtime worked\n"
"            - Benefits in kind and bonuses\n"
"            - Remuneration of statutory holidays occurring within 30 days of "
"the end date of the contract\n"
"            - End-of-year bonus, 13th month or other similar amount\n"
"            - Beneficiary holdings\n"
"            - Various bonuses\n"
"        We draw your attention to the fact that this information is based on "
"the data in Odoo and / or that you\n"
"        have introduced in Odoo and that it is important that they be "
"accompanied by a verification on your part\n"
"        according to the particularities related to contract of the worker "
"or your company which Odoo would not\n"
"        know.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        In aanmerking genomen voor de bezoldiging:\n"
"- Vaste en variabele bezoldiging\n"
"- Gewerkte overuren\n"
"- Voordelen van alle aard en bonussen\n"
"- Vergoeding van wettelijke feestdagen die binnen 30 dagen na de einddatum "
"van het contract vallen\n"
"- Eindejaarsbonus, 13e maand of ander soortgelijk bedrag\n"
"- Bezittingen van begunstigden\n"
"- Diverse bonussen\n"
"Wij wijzen je erop dat deze informatie is gebaseerd op de gegevens in Odoo "
"en/of die je\n"
"in Odoo hebt ingevoerd en dat het belangrijk is dat je deze controleert\n"
"aan de hand van de bijzonderheden met betrekking tot het contract van de "
"werknemer of je bedrijf, die Odoo niet\n"
"kent.\n"
"        "

