#. module: l10n_be_hr_payroll
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/l10n_be_hr_payroll/models/hr_employee.py:0
msgid ""
"- High Income: Spouse earns more than %(low_income_threshold)s€ net/month.\n"
"\n"
"- Low Income: Spouse earns between %(no_income_threshold)s€ and %"
"(low_income_threshold)s€ net/month.\n"
"\n"
"- Without Income: Spouse earns less than %(no_income_threshold)s€ net/"
"month.\n"
"\n"
"- High Pensions : Spouse is eligible to a pension higher than %"
"(other_income_threshold)s€ net/month.\n"
"\n"
"- Low Pensions : Spouse is eligible to a pension lower than %"
"(other_income_threshold)s€ net/month.\n"
"\n"
"Earnings are made of professional income, remuneration, unemployment "
"allocations, annuities or similar income."
msgstr ""
"- Hoog inkomen: Echtgeno(o)t(e) verdient meer dan € %(low_income_threshold)s "
"netto per maand.\n"
"\n"
"- Laag inkomen: Echtgeno(o)t(e) verdient tussen € %(no_income_threshold)s en "
"€ %(low_income_threshold)s netto per maand.\n"
"\n"
"- Zonder inkomen: Echtgeno(o)t(e) verdient minder dan € %"
"(no_income_threshold)s netto per maand.\n"
"\n"
"- Hoog pensioen: Echtgeno(o)t(e) komt in aanmerking voor een pensioen van "
"meer dan € %(other_income_threshold)s netto per maand.\n"
"\n"
"- Laag pensioen: Echtgeno(o)t(e) komt in aanmerking voor een pensioen van "
"minder dan € %(other_income_threshold)s netto per maand.\n"
"\n"
"Inkomsten bestaan uit beroepsinkomsten, vergoedingen, "
"werkloosheidsuitkeringen, lijfrentes of soortgelijke inkomsten."

